%   hist:  historical primary or scholarly historical sources
%   text:  classical handbooks and established textbooks
%   paper: peer-reviewed research papers and conference proceedings
%   data:  datasets and empirical compilations
%   web:   institutional / online primary sources
%   gen:   cross-book influences (works that shape the project as a whole)
%
% Within a category, entries are alphabetical by key. Sub-section comments
% may further organise by domain when an entry count makes that useful.

